#. <section class="sutta" id="sn15.3"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn15.3:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 15"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 15"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn15.3:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga"
msgstr "1. The First Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn15.3:0.3"
msgid "3. Assusutta"
msgstr "3. Tears"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi2.180"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn15.3:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn15.3:1.2"
msgid "“Anamataggoyaṃ, bhikkhave, saṃsāro."
msgstr "“Mendicants, transmigration has no known beginning."

msgctxt "sn15.3:1.3"
msgid ""
"Pubbā koṭi na paññāyati avijjānīvaraṇānaṃ sattānaṃ taṇhāsaṃyojanānaṃ "
"sandhāvataṃ saṃsarataṃ."
msgstr ""
"No first point is found of sentient beings roaming and transmigrating, "
"hindered by ignorance and fettered by craving."

#. VAR: rodantānaṃ → rudantānaṃ (bj)
#. VAR: passannaṃ → passandaṃ (si) | pasandaṃ (s1-3, km) | pasannaṃ (pts1-2, mr)
msgctxt "sn15.3:1.4"
msgid ""
"Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, katamaṃ nu kho bahutaraṃ, yaṃ vā vo iminā "
"dīghena addhunā sandhāvataṃ saṃsarataṃ amanāpasampayogā manāpavippayogā "
"kandantānaṃ rodantānaṃ assu passannaṃ paggharitaṃ, yaṃ vā catūsu "
"mahāsamuddesu udakan”ti?"
msgstr ""
"What do you think? Which is more: the flow of tears you’ve shed while "
"roaming and transmigrating for such a very long time—weeping and wailing "
"from being united with the unloved and separated from the loved—or the water "
"in the four oceans?”"

msgctxt "sn15.3:1.5"
msgid ""
"“Yathā kho mayaṃ, bhante, bhagavatā dhammaṃ desitaṃ ājānāma, etadeva, "
"bhante, bahutaraṃ yaṃ no iminā dīghena addhunā sandhāvataṃ saṃsarataṃ "
"amanāpasampayogā manāpavippayogā kandantānaṃ rodantānaṃ assu passannaṃ "
"paggharitaṃ, na tveva catūsu mahāsamuddesu udakan”ti."
msgstr ""
"“As we understand the Buddha’s teaching, the flow of tears we’ve shed while "
"roaming and transmigrating is more than the water in the four oceans.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn15.3:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Sādhu sādhu, bhikkhave, sādhu kho me tumhe, bhikkhave, evaṃ dhammaṃ desitaṃ "
"ājānātha."
msgstr ""
"“Good, good, mendicants! It’s good that you understand my teaching like this."

msgctxt "sn15.3:2.2"
msgid ""
"Etadeva, bhikkhave, bahutaraṃ yaṃ vo iminā dīghena addhunā sandhāvataṃ "
"saṃsarataṃ amanāpasampayogā manāpavippayogā kandantānaṃ rodantānaṃ assu "
"passannaṃ paggharitaṃ, na tveva catūsu mahāsamuddesu udakaṃ."
msgstr ""
"The flow of tears you’ve shed while roaming and transmigrating is indeed "
"more than the water in the four oceans."

msgctxt "sn15.3:2.3"
msgid "Dīgharattaṃ vo, bhikkhave, mātumaraṇaṃ paccanubhūtaṃ;"
msgstr "For a long time you’ve undergone the death of a mother …"

msgctxt "sn15.3:2.4"
msgid ""
"tesaṃ vo mātumaraṇaṃ paccanubhontānaṃ amanāpasampayogā manāpavippayogā "
"kandantānaṃ rodantānaṃ assu passannaṃ paggharitaṃ, na tveva catūsu "
"mahāsamuddesu udakaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn15.3:2.5"
msgid "Dīgharattaṃ vo, bhikkhave, pitumaraṇaṃ paccanubhūtaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "father …"

msgctxt "sn15.3:2.6"
msgid "bhātumaraṇaṃ paccanubhūtaṃ …"
msgstr "brother …"

msgctxt "sn15.3:2.7"
msgid "bhaginimaraṇaṃ paccanubhūtaṃ …"
msgstr "sister …"

msgctxt "sn15.3:2.8"
msgid "puttamaraṇaṃ paccanubhūtaṃ …"
msgstr "son …"

msgctxt "sn15.3:2.9"
msgid "dhītumaraṇaṃ paccanubhūtaṃ …"
msgstr "daughter …"

msgctxt "sn15.3:2.10"
msgid "ñātibyasanaṃ paccanubhūtaṃ …"
msgstr "loss of relatives …"

msgctxt "sn15.3:2.11"
msgid "bhogabyasanaṃ paccanubhūtaṃ."
msgstr "loss of wealth …"

msgctxt "sn15.3:2.12"
msgid ""
"Dīgharattaṃ vo, bhikkhave, rogabyasanaṃ paccanubhūtaṃ, tesaṃ vo rogabyasanaṃ "
"paccanubhontānaṃ amanāpasampayogā manāpavippayogā kandantānaṃ rodantānaṃ "
"assu passannaṃ paggharitaṃ, na tveva catūsu mahāsamuddesu udakaṃ."
msgstr ""
"or loss through illness. From being united with the unloved and separated "
"from the loved, the flow of tears you’ve shed while roaming and "
"transmigrating is indeed more than the water in the four oceans."

msgctxt "sn15.3:2.13"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "sn15.3:2.14"
msgid "Anamataggoyaṃ, bhikkhave, saṃsāro … pe …"
msgstr "Transmigration has no known beginning. …"

msgctxt "sn15.3:2.15"
msgid ""
"yāvañcidaṃ, bhikkhave, alameva sabbasaṅkhāresu nibbindituṃ, alaṃ virajjituṃ, "
"alaṃ vimuccitun”ti."
msgstr ""
"This is quite enough for you to become disillusioned, dispassionate, and "
"freed regarding all conditions.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn15.3:2.16"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
